Hello KSP watcher and/or Youtuber. Finally, after a 1 week delay my KSP video is out at: http://youtu.be/zwuStIeHOiY.

This episode we launch a rocket into LKO, dock with space station "Kerbal" and do stuff. PLEASE WATCH the whole video but if that is too much skip around to the end of the video. No I don't want to tell you and spoil it, go and see it !

If you got here by random or don't know me, you can get to know me at my fourm page at: http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/members/85583-It-snorocketscience

Or see my YouTube homepage at: http://www.youtube.com/channel/UCf1u...VmzBc8Q/videos.

I hope you enjoy my 5th episode!
